<div class="modal fade" id="<%= id %>" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="Book CSV Modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-sm" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title">
          Upload Book CSV file
        </h5>
        <a href="#" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></a>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Use this feature to upload a CSV of books that you wish to see in the app.</p>
        <p>This will not replace existing books, only adding books that do not already exist in the app.</p>
        <p>The CSV file must include the following data - all being integers except for Title (string, capitalized) and Purchased (true/false):</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Title</li>
          <li>Author ID</li>
          <li>Genre ID</li>
          <li>Rating</li>
          <li>Series ID</li>
          <li>Series Position</li>
          <li>Total Pages</li>
          <li>Purchased</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To do this, make an Excel file containing the books data, then convert the file to CSV before uploading.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
